                    <formatted-text>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>📌 Key Insights:</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• Inactive customers show significantly higher churn</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• Customers with only one product are more likely to leave</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• Churn is highest during early tenure</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• Certain regions with high-balance customers show elevated churn risk</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>📌 Recommendations:</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• Improve onboarding for new customers</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• Increase engagement through targeted campaigns</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• Focus on cross-selling additional products</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>• Investigate high-value churn segments</run>
                    </formatted-text>
